=== README.md ===
1:# MeridianCare Outpatient Operations
2:
3:On-prem fullstack platform for clinic encounters, e-prescriptions, pharmacy/inventory operations, billing, credentialing, crawler ingestion, forecasting lifecycle, and backup/restore drills.
4:
5:## Architecture Map
6:- `backend/`: Fastify API modules (`auth`, `patients`, `encounters`, `prescriptions`, `inventory`, `billing`, `credentialing`, `admin`, `sync_audit`) with PostgreSQL persistence.
7:- `frontend/`: Angular desktop-first role workspaces (Physician, Pharmacist, Billing, Inventory, Admin, Auditor).
8:- `backend/tests/unit_tests`: unit tests for core logic (security, discounts, allergy checks, state machine, masking, logging).
9:- `backend/tests/API_tests`: API and E2E acceptance tests by requirement/phase.
10:- `docs/requirements_traceability.md`: requirement-to-implementation and requirement-to-test matrix (1-41).
11:
12:## One-Click Startup (Docker)
13:```bash
14:docker compose up --build
15:```
16:
17:- Frontend: http://localhost:14200
18:- Backend health: http://localhost:13000/health
19:
20:## Verification (Docker-only)
21:Run full suite:
22:
23:```bash
24:./run_tests.sh
25:```
26:
27:Individual checks:
28:
29:
30:## Security and Data Isolation
31:- Local username/password auth only; minimum password length 12; bcrypt hashing.
32:- Lockout policy: 5 failed attempts -> 15-minute lockout.
33:- Session idle timeout: 20 minutes with session revocation support.
34:- RBAC route checks for Physician/Pharmacist/Billing/Inventory/Admin/Auditor.
35:- PHI controls: encrypted sensitive identifiers and masked patient projections for non-clinical views.
36:- Audit immutability: encounter/prescription/credentialing edits emit append-only audit events with snapshots.
37:- Concurrency protections: optimistic version checks + transactional `SELECT ... FOR UPDATE` on dispense.
38:- Payments are manual records only (`cash/card/manual_ref`) with no external payment gateway integration.
39:
40:## Seeded Local Users
41:- `physician@local` (`physician`)
42:- `pharmacist@local` (`pharmacist`)
43:- `billing@local` (`billing`)
44:- `inventory@local` (`inventory`)
45:- `admin@local` (`admin`)
46:- `auditor@local` (`auditor`)
47:
48:Default password: `Password!123` (override with `SEED_PASSWORD` env var).
